Senso4s Homey App

This app includes Senso4s BLE protocol parsing and characteristic handling
adapted from the Senso4s Home Assistant integration:

  https://github.com/ksanislo/senso4s_ble

The referenced integration is Copyright 2026 Ken Sanislo and licensed under
the Apache License, Version 2.0.

Changes for this app include porting the parser and BLE client behavior from
Python/Home Assistant to TypeScript/Homey SDK 3, mapping values to Homey
capabilities, and adapting the pairing and polling lifecycle for Homey.
